    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="MYSQL函数"><a href="#MYSQL函数" class="headerlink" title="MYSQL函数"></a>MYSQL函数</h1><h5 id="mysql-connect-—-打开一个到-MySQL-服务器的连接"><a href="#mysql-connect-—-打开一个到-MySQL-服务器的连接" class="headerlink" title="mysql_connect — 打开一个到 MySQL 服务器的连接"></a>mysql_connect — 打开一个到 MySQL 服务器的连接</h5><h5 id="mysql-close-—-关闭-MySQL-连接"><a href="#mysql-close-—-关闭-MySQL-连接" class="headerlink" title="mysql_close — 关闭 MySQL 连接"></a>mysql_close — 关闭 MySQL 连接</h5><p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/18.png" alt="18"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-query-—-发送一条-MySQL-查询"><a href="#mysql-query-—-发送一条-MySQL-查询" class="headerlink" title="mysql_query — 发送一条 MySQL 查询"></a>mysql_query — 发送一条 MySQL 查询</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$link = mysql_connect(<span class="string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(!$link)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Could not connect :&#x27;</span> . mysql_error());</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$sql = <span class="string">&#x27;CREATE DATABASE my_db&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (mysql_query($sql, $link))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;Database my_db created successfully&quot;</span>.<span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;Error creating database &quot;</span>.mysql_error().<span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">mysql_close($link);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/19.PNG" alt="19"></p>
<h5 id="error-reporting-—-设置应该报告何种-PHP-错误"><a href="#error-reporting-—-设置应该报告何种-PHP-错误" class="headerlink" title="error_reporting() — 设置应该报告何种 PHP 错误"></a>error_reporting() — 设置应该报告何种 PHP 错误</h5><h5 id="mysql-list-dbs-—-列出MYSQL服务器中所有的数据库"><a href="#mysql-list-dbs-—-列出MYSQL服务器中所有的数据库" class="headerlink" title="mysql_list_dbs() — 列出MYSQL服务器中所有的数据库"></a>mysql_list_dbs() — 列出MYSQL服务器中所有的数据库</h5><h5 id="mysql-num-rows-—-取得结果集中行的数目"><a href="#mysql-num-rows-—-取得结果集中行的数目" class="headerlink" title="mysql_num_rows() —  取得结果集中行的数目"></a>mysql_num_rows() —  取得结果集中行的数目</h5><h5 id="mysql-db-name-—-取得结果数据"><a href="#mysql-db-name-—-取得结果数据" class="headerlink" title="mysql_db_name() — 取得结果数据"></a>mysql_db_name() — 取得结果数据</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">error_reporting(E_ALL);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$link = mysql_connect(<span class="string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$db_list = mysql_list_dbs($link);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$i = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$cnt = mysql_num_rows($db_list);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> ($i &lt; $cnt)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> mysql_db_name($db_list, $i).<span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	$i++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/21.PNG" alt="21"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-escape-string"><a href="#mysql-escape-string" class="headerlink" title="mysql_escape_string()"></a>mysql_escape_string()</h5><h6 id="mysql-escape-string-—-转义一个字符串用于-mysql-query"><a href="#mysql-escape-string-—-转义一个字符串用于-mysql-query" class="headerlink" title="mysql_escape_string — 转义一个字符串用于 mysql_query"></a>mysql_escape_string — 转义一个字符串用于 mysql_query</h6><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">	$itm = <span class="string">&quot;Cat&#x27;s&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	$escaped_item = mysql_escape_string($itm);</span><br><span class="line">	printf (<span class="string">&quot;Escaped string :%s\n&quot;</span>,$escaped_item)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/22.PNG" alt="22"></p>
<h6 id="mysql-fetch-array-—-从结果集中取得一行作为关联数组，或数字数组，或二者兼有"><a href="#mysql-fetch-array-—-从结果集中取得一行作为关联数组，或数字数组，或二者兼有" class="headerlink" title="mysql_fetch_array — 从结果集中取得一行作为关联数组，或数字数组，或二者兼有"></a>mysql_fetch_array — 从结果集中取得一行作为关联数组，或数字数组，或二者兼有</h6><h6 id="mysql-free-result-—-释放结果内存-成功时返回-TRUE-，-或者在失败时返回-FALSE"><a href="#mysql-free-result-—-释放结果内存-成功时返回-TRUE-，-或者在失败时返回-FALSE" class="headerlink" title="mysql_free_result — 释放结果内存,成功时返回 TRUE**， 或者在失败时返回 **FALSE"></a>mysql_free_result — 释放结果内存,成功时返回 <strong><code>TRUE</code>**， 或者在失败时返回 **<code>FALSE</code></strong></h6><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">	mysql_connect(<span class="string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">or</span> </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Could not connect: &quot;</span>. mysql_error());</span><br><span class="line">	mysql_select_db(<span class="string">&quot;mysql&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	$result = mysql_query(<span class="string">&quot;SELECT User,Host FROM user&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">while</span> ($row = mysql_fetch_array($result, MYSQL_NUM))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		printf(<span class="string">&quot;user:%s\nHost:%s&quot;</span>,$row[<span class="number">0</span>],$row[<span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&lt;br&gt;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	mysql_free_result($result);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/20.PNG" alt="20"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-fetch-object-—-从结果集中取得一行作为对象"><a href="#mysql-fetch-object-—-从结果集中取得一行作为对象" class="headerlink" title="mysql_fetch_object — 从结果集中取得一行作为对象"></a>mysql_fetch_object — 从结果集中取得一行作为对象</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">mysql_connect(<span class="string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">mysql_select_db(<span class="string">&quot;mysql&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$result = mysql_query(<span class="string">&quot;select User,Host from user&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> ($row = mysql_fetch_object($result)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;User:&quot;</span>.$row-&gt;User;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;\r&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;Host:&quot;</span>.$row-&gt;Host;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&lt;br&gt;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">mysql_free_result($result);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/23.PNG" alt="23"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-fetch-row-—-从结果集中取得一行作为枚举数组"><a href="#mysql-fetch-row-—-从结果集中取得一行作为枚举数组" class="headerlink" title="mysql_fetch_row — 从结果集中取得一行作为枚举数组"></a>mysql_fetch_row — 从结果集中取得一行作为枚举数组</h5><h6 id="返回根据所取得的行生成的数组，如果没有更多行则返回-FALSE"><a href="#返回根据所取得的行生成的数组，如果没有更多行则返回-FALSE" class="headerlink" title="返回根据所取得的行生成的数组，如果没有更多行则返回 FALSE"></a>返回根据所取得的行生成的数组，如果没有更多行则返回 <strong><code>FALSE</code></strong></h6><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">mysql_connect(<span class="string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">mysql_select_db(<span class="string">&quot;mysql&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$result = mysql_query(<span class="string">&quot;SELECT User,Host from user&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!$result)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Could not run query:&#x27;</span>.mysql_error();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">$row = mysql_fetch_row($result);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> $row[<span class="number">0</span>].<span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;	<span class="comment">//User</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> $row[<span class="number">1</span>];		<span class="comment">//Host			</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/24.PNG" alt="24"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-get-client-info-—-取得-MySQL-客户端信息"><a href="#mysql-get-client-info-—-取得-MySQL-客户端信息" class="headerlink" title="mysql_get_client_info — 取得 MySQL 客户端信息"></a>mysql_get_client_info — 取得 MySQL 客户端信息</h5><h5 id="mysql-get-host-info-—-取得-MySQL-主机信息"><a href="#mysql-get-host-info-—-取得-MySQL-主机信息" class="headerlink" title="mysql_get_host_info — 取得 MySQL 主机信息"></a>mysql_get_host_info — 取得 MySQL 主机信息</h5><h5 id="mysql-get-proto-info-—-取得-MySQL-协议信息"><a href="#mysql-get-proto-info-—-取得-MySQL-协议信息" class="headerlink" title="mysql_get_proto_info — 取得 MySQL 协议信息"></a>mysql_get_proto_info — 取得 MySQL 协议信息</h5><h5 id="mysql-get-server-info-—-取得-MySQL-服务器信息"><a href="#mysql-get-server-info-—-取得-MySQL-服务器信息" class="headerlink" title="mysql_get_server_info — 取得 MySQL 服务器信息"></a>mysql_get_server_info — 取得 MySQL 服务器信息</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">mysql_connect(<span class="string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">mysql_select_db(<span class="string">&quot;mysql&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$result = mysql_query(<span class="string">&quot;SELECT User,Host from user&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">printf (<span class="string">&quot;MySQL client info:%s\n&quot;</span>,mysql_get_client_info());	</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">printf (<span class="string">&quot;Mysql host info:%s\n&quot;</span>,mysql_get_host_info());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">printf (<span class="string">&quot;Mysql protocol version:%s\n&quot;</span>,mysql_get_proto_info());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">printf (<span class="string">&quot;Mysql server version:%s\n&quot;</span>,mysql_get_server_info());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/25.PNG" alt="25"></p>
<h5 id="mysql-list-fields-—-列出-MySQL-结果中的字段"><a href="#mysql-list-fields-—-列出-MySQL-结果中的字段" class="headerlink" title="mysql_list_fields — 列出 MySQL 结果中的字段"></a>mysql_list_fields — 列出 MySQL 结果中的字段</h5><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line">$link = mysql_connect(<span class="string">&#x27;localhost&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">$fields = mysql_list_fields(<span class="string">&quot;mysql&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;user&quot;</span>,$link);</span><br><span class="line">$columns = mysql_num_fields($fields);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> ($i=<span class="number">0</span>; $i &lt; $columns; $i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">echo</span> mysql_field_name($fields,$i).<span class="string">&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://ey404.github.io/2020/09/26/26.PNG" alt="26"></p>
<p>mysql_db_query — 发送一条 MySQL 查询</p>
<p>mysql_drop_db — 丢弃（删除）一个 MySQL 数据库</p>
<p>mysql_fetch_assoc — 从结果集中取得一行作为关联数组     </p>
<p>mysql_fetch_field — 从结果集中取得列信息并作为对象返回 </p>
<p>mysql_fetch_lengths — 取得结果集中每个输出的长度</p>
<p>mysql_list_processes — 列出 MySQL 进程</p>
<p>mysql_list_tables — 列出 MySQL 数据库中的表 </p>
<p>mysql_pconnect — 打开一个到 MySQL 服务器的持久连接 </p>
]]></content>
